In the second example, you'll
see there's a light gray background,

00:27:32.280 --> 00:27:35.360
and then there's privacy
policy, terms and conditions,

00:27:35.360 --> 00:27:38.616
disclaimer, affiliate terms and
conditions, and cookie policy.

00:27:38.640 --> 00:27:42.400
All of them are separated
and they are in dark purple font.

00:27:42.840 --> 00:27:44.490
So they're very easily visible.

00:27:44.490 --> 00:27:46.906
They're not hidden.

00:27:49.012 --> 00:27:52.070
<v Hans> All right. So it’s also
important to understand that

00:27:52.070 --> 00:27:53.660
whenever someone’s
submitting their data,

00:27:53.660 --> 00:27:55.386
it is considered
a best practice.

00:27:55.410 --> 00:27:58.076
And under some privacy
laws, it's a legal requirement

00:27:58.100 --> 00:28:01.560
to ensure that people are
checking a box to agree

00:28:01.560 --> 00:28:06.016
to your privacy policy, and checking
another box to agree to your terms.

00:28:06.040 --> 00:28:09.730
So as you'll see in this example,
this website has a contact

00:28:09.730 --> 00:28:11.850
form asking for
