00:28:35.760 --> 00:28:39.696
This is very important from a
privacy compliance standpoint.

00:28:39.720 --> 00:28:43.200
You need to capture consent,
the moment people agree.

00:28:43.200 --> 00:28:46.656
So that is why those check
boxes are required fields,

00:28:46.680 --> 00:28:48.920
but you actually have check
them to be able to submit your data.

00:28:49.312 --> 00:28:51.828
<v Donata> Yes, exactly.

00:28:53.880 --> 00:28:56.690
So in this next form,
