00:29:17.460 --> 00:29:21.150
because it is not providing a
privacy policy, and it does not link

00:29:21.170 --> 00:29:22.480
to a privacy policy.

00:29:22.880 --> 00:29:25.900
So here, even though they're
obtaining consent for their newsletter,

00:29:25.900 --> 00:29:28.836
which is great, they should
also have another box that says,

00:29:28.860 --> 00:29:32.630
I agree to the privacy policy
because their data is being collected.

00:29:34.964 --> 00:29:38.040
<v Hans> We probably should
