00:29:40.520 --> 00:29:43.000
But do you want
to take this one?

00:29:43.000 --> 00:29:43.936
<v Donata> Sure.

00:29:43.960 --> 00:29:47.746
So this is an example of
the text of the privacy policy.

00:29:47.770 --> 00:29:50.016
So the first one says,
